  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will campaign on Oxfam&apos;s global campaigns in Scotland. To include Economic Justice and Essential Services. We will seek to influence Scottish, UK and where possible global debates relevant to these campaigns. This will include targeting the Scottish &amp; UK Parliament&apos;s , engaging with the Scottish public, media, politicians, education sector, and where appropriate, with the private sector. We will also support Oxfam&apos;s corporate objectives, including giving media and lobbying support relevant to humanitarian fundraising, community fundraising, the UK Poverty Programme and Fundraising Partnerships.</narrative>
